/blue-flag-beaches-malta`, both inside the existing `BrandedRoutes` switch so they sit under `BrandGuard`) and added 'Malta Resources' to `SidebarLayout.tsx` directly under 'Sicily Resources' using the same `MapPin` icon for symmetry. No existing routes or sidebar items were moved."]	2026-05-15 11:40:05.306004+00	1
