8	4	https://www.virtuferries.com/commercial_vehicles/14	Virtu Ferries - Commercial Vehicles	Commercial Vehicles\n \n \n \n \n \n \nIncrease your margins & be competitive with Virtu Ferries\n\nThe Virtu Ferries fast passenger and vehicle ferries, reach Pozzallo in under two hours, and Catania in just over three hours, with daily trips all year round.\nAdditionally, commercial clients and transporters, have the possibility of fast day return accompanied cargo service from/to both Pozzallo and Catania, any day of the week.\nCommercial vehicles up to 19 metres in length (45 Tons maximum load), depart from Malta early in the morning on a daily basis, and the vehicles are back in Malta the same evening. Cargo departing from Pozzallo on our morning trips at 09.15, or from Catania at 0500hrs, is unloaded in Malta that same morning, and vehicles are back home in Sicily by early evening. Same day, short transit time is our hallmark.\nThe daily return schedule and short transit time have proved invaluable for various types of perishable and other time sensitive cargo, with the added advantage that the same vehicle can come and go on a daily basis between the two neighbouring islands.\nAccredited transporters provide for any kind of cargo, delivered straight to your destination, from the Virtu high speed ferries.\nMOVE YOUR CARGO FAST. TIME IS MONEY. MAKE DAILY USE OF YOUR TRANSPORT VEHICLE. GO VIRTU.\n\nOur online flyer showcases the key benefits of our service, including speed, reliability and customer testimonials. Discover why Virtu Ferries is the fastest and most efficient freight service between Malta and Sicily. Download the flyer.\n \n\nOFFER ON COMMERCIAL VEHICLES UP TO 5.9m - as from 1st January 2026\nUp to 4.5m return - From €413 + €67.60 (ETS)\nUp to 5.0m return - From €520 + €74.60 (ETS)\nUp to 5.5m return - From €581 + €81.60 (ETS)\nUp to 5.9m return - From €676 + €88.60 (ETS)\nThe above fares include all charges, incl. the vehicle driver's ticket. Not applicable 