56	4	https://www.virtuferries.com/news/virtu_ferries_mobile_app/20	Virtu Ferries - News detail	Travel Made Simpler with the Virtu Ferries App\n \nWhether you're planning a trip to Sicily or managing your travel experience, the Virtu Ferries app is the perfect travel companion. With its easy-to-use features and user-friendly interface, the app makes managing your travel plans a breeze. All you need to do is create an account or log in with your existing one to explore all the features available at your fingertips.\nHere's everything you can do on the Virtu Ferries app:\nBoarding Passes: No need to worry about printing out your boarding pass or forgetting your tickets at home. The Virtu Ferries app lets you easily access your e-tickets and boarding passes on your phone. This feature saves you time and eliminates the need for physical tickets.\nCreate New Bookings: Booking your ferry tickets has never been easier! With just a few taps, you can create new bookings and choose your preferred travel dates and times. The app also shows you all available ticket options, so you can find the best deal for your budget.\nView Past & Future Bookings: Keep track of your ferry travel history and future bookings with the app. You can view your past and future bookings anytime, anywhere.\nEdit Bookings: Need to make changes to your booking? No problem! The Virtu Ferries app allows you to easily edit your bookings and make changes to your travel plans.\nBe The First To Know: Be the first to know about offers, promotions, and discounts on various products and services including travel, shopping centers, and accommodations.\nView Schedule: Want to know when the next ferry is departing? The app allows you to check the schedules of all available routes so that you can plan your journey accordingly.\nManage Your Profile: The app provides a convenient and accessible way to manage your profile. You can update your personal information, view your travel history, and manage your notifications all in one place.\nDownload the app on May 9th from the Apple App Store or Google Play and get ready to explore the wonders of Sicily with ease.	200	2	2026-04-25 14:54:57.673636+00
