37	4	https://www.virtuferries.com/family/60	Virtu Ferries - Family	Family\n \n \n \n \n \n \n\nFamily Holiday\nMalta is just great for a family holiday. For a start, you are never very far from where you want to be and the short distances means you can do more than just one thing in a day. The island is safe. The sight of young families and old ladies strolling along in the late evenings is testimony to this. Outdoor living is a way of life, more or less throughout the year.\n\nWhat to do:\nOutdoor Fun\n\nLots of beaches to choose from\nHorse riding \nPopeye Village, join the Popeye gang \nMediterraneo Marine Park, join the dolphins and sea lions. \n\nAdd to the family’s culture experience:\n\nThe unique Neolithic\nEsplora, a superb interactive science centre \n\nIndoor fun\n\nMalta National Aquarium\n\nFor the little ones:\n\nPlaymobil Fun Park\n\nHealth\n\nWe strongly recommend you visit our section on Health.	200	2	2026-04-25 14:54:54.436832+00
